Headstrong/Firedrill/Cliffjumper

Headstrong tries to maneuver out of the way. Two of the blasts hit him
in the head, but he turns around, and two hit Firedrill. THey both
collapse.

Cliffjumper looking on sees Firedrill fall, and assumes Gimler was
firing on him in the first place. "Why you backstabber" he yelled, and
transformed into his car mode, quickly eccxellerating to 300mph in a
second and heads straight at Gimller's feet.
